title: Match history Doesnt show up in the Website(why)?

replies.body: This ma be a caching issue, so forcing a refresh via Ctrl + R may help as well as clearing your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies).  I'm also not sure what url you're going to based on that screen, but here is the one for [your profile.](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/45742016)  :D  I hope that helps!
